\c 7
\s Iminikelo enikelelwa ilathi
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ngosuku uMozisi aqeda ngalo ukumisa ithabhanekele\x + Eks. 40.17,18. Levi 8.10,11. Nani 6.10.\x*, waligcoba\x + Eks. 40.17,18. Levi 8.10,11. Nani 7.10.\x*, walingcwelisa, lempahla zalo zonke, lelathi lempahla zalo zonke, wakugcoba, wakungcwelisa;
\v 2 iziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli, izinhloko zezindlu zaboyise, ezaziyiziphathamandla zezizwe, ezazisongamela labo ababalwayo\x + 1.4.\x*, zanikela,
\v 3 zaletha umnikelo wazo phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, inqola eziyisithupha ezembesiweyo\x + Isa. 66.20.\x* lenkabi ezilitshumi lambili; inqola eyodwa ngeziphathamandla ezimbili, lenkabi ngesisodwa; zazisondeza phambi kwethabhanekele.
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 5 Yemukela kuzo, ukuze zibe ngezokusebenza inkonzo yethente lenhlangano, uzinike amaLevi, kulowo lalowo njengomsebenzi wakhe.
\v 6 Ngakho uMozisi wathatha izinqola lezinkabi, wazinika amaLevi.
\v 7 Inqola ezimbili lenkabi ezine wazinika amadodana kaGerishoni, njengomsebenzi wawo\x + 4.25,28.\x*;
\v 8 lenqola ezine lenkabi eziyisificaminwembili wazinika amadodana kaMerari, njengomsebenzi wawo\x + 4.29,31,33.\x*, ngesandla sikaIthamari indodana kaAroni umpristi.
\v 9 Kodwa emadodaneni kaKohathi kanikanga \add lutho\add*, ngoba umsebenzi wendawo engcwele wawuphezu kwawo\x + 4.15.\x*, awuthwala emahlombe\x + 4.4-15; 2 Sam. 6.13.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Leziphathamandla zanikelela ukwehlukaniselwa kwelathi ngosuku elagcotshwa ngalo\x + 7.84,88. Dute. 20.5. 1 Kho. 8.63. 2 Lan. 7.5,9. Ezra 6.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*; iziphathamandla zasondeza umnikelo wazo phambi kwelathi.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi kuMozisi: Isiphathamandla ngasinye ngasinye ngosuku lwaso, zizanikelela umnikelo wazo wokwehlukaniselwa kwelathi\x + 7.84,88. Dute. 20.5. 1 Kho. 8.63. 2 Lan. 7.5,9. Ezra 6.16. Neh. 12.27.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Owanikela-ke umnikelo wakhe ngosuku lokuqala wayenguNashoni indodana kaAminadaba, owesizwe sakoJuda\x + 1.7.\x*.
\v 13 Lomnikelo wakhe wawungumganu owodwa wesiliva, osisindo sawo sasingama\add \w shekeli\w**\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amathathu\x + Eks. 30.13.\x*, umganu wokufafaza owodwa wesiliva wamashekeli angamatshumi ayisikhombisa, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele\x + Eks. 30.13.\x*; yomibili yayigcwele impuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, kube ngumnikelo wokudla\x + Levi 2.1,4; Nani 8.8.\x*;
\v 14 ukhezo olulodwa olungama\add shekeli\add* alitshumi egolide, lugcwele impepha\x + Eks. 30.34.\x*;
\v 15 ijongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo, inqama eyodwa, iwundlu elilodwa elilomnyaka owodwa, kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa\x + Levi 1.2,3.\x*;
\v 16 izinyane lembuzi elilodwa libe ngumnikelo wesono\x + Levi 4.23,24.\x*;
\v 17 lokomhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula, izinkabi ezimbili, inqama ezinhlanu, impongo ezinhlanu, amawundlu amahlanu alomnyaka owodwa\x + Levi 3.1.\x*. Lokhu kwakungumnikelo kaNashoni indodana kaAminadaba.
\p
\v 18 Ngosuku lwesibili uNethaneli indodana kaZuwari, isiphathamandla sakoIsakari, wanikela\x + 1.8.\x*.
\v 19 Wanikela umnikelo wakhe: Umganu owodwa wesiliva, osisindo sawo sasingama\add shekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amathathu, umganu wokufafaza owodwa wesiliva wamashekeli angamatshumi ayisikhombisa, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele; yomibili yayigcwele impuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, kube ngumnikelo wokudla;
\v 20 ukhezo olulodwa olungama\add shekeli\add* alitshumi egolide, lugcwele impepha;
\v 21 ijongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo, inqama eyodwa, iwundlu elilodwa elilomnyaka owodwa, kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa;
\v 22 izinyane lembuzi elilodwa libe ngumnikelo wesono;
\v 23 lokomhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula, izinkabi ezimbili, inqama ezinhlanu, impongo ezinhlanu, amawundlu amahlanu alomnyaka owodwa. Lokhu kwakungumnikelo kaNethaneli indodana kaZuwari.
\p
\v 24 Ngosuku lwesithathu uEliyabi indodana kaHeloni, isiphathamandla sabantwana bakoZebuluni\x + 1.9.\x*:
\v 25 Umnikelo wakhe wawungumganu owodwa wesiliva, osisindo sawo sasingama\add shekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amathathu, umganu wokufafaza owodwa wesiliva wamashekeli angamatshumi ayisikhombisa, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele; yomibili yayigcwele impuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, kube ngumnikelo wokudla;
\v 26 ukhezo olulodwa olungama\add shekeli\add* alitshumi egolide, lugcwele impepha;
\v 27 ijongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo, inqama eyodwa, iwundlu elilodwa elilomnyaka owodwa, kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa;
\v 28 izinyane lembuzi elilodwa libe ngumnikelo wesono;
\v 29 lokomhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula, izinkabi ezimbili, inqama ezinhlanu, impongo ezinhlanu, amawundlu amahlanu alomnyaka owodwa. Lokho kwakungumnikelo kaEliyabi indodana kaHeloni.
\p
\v 30 Ngosuku lwesine uElizuri indodana kaShedewuri, isiphathamandla sabantwana bakoRubeni\x + 1.5.\x*:
\v 31 Umnikelo wakhe wawungumganu owodwa wesiliva, osisindo sawo sasingama\add shekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amathathu, umganu wokufafaza owodwa wesiliva wamashekeli angamatshumi ayisikhombisa, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele; yomibili yayigcwele impuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, kube ngumnikelo wokudla;
