\v 78 Ngosuku lwetshumi lambili uAhira indodana kaEnani, isiphathamandla sabantwana bakoNafithali\x + 1.15.\x*:
\v 79 Umnikelo wakhe wawungumganu owodwa wesiliva, osisindo sawo sasingama\add shekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amathathu, umganu wokufafaza owodwa wesiliva wamashekeli angamatshumi ayisikhombisa, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele; yomibili yayigcwele impuphu ecolekileyo ixubene lamafutha, kube ngumnikelo wokudla;
\v 80 ukhezo olulodwa olungama\add shekeli\add* alitshumi egolide, lugcwele impepha;
\v 81 ijongosi elilodwa ithole lenkomo, inqama eyodwa, iwundlu elilodwa elilomnyaka owodwa, kube ngumnikelo wokutshiswa;
\v 82 izinyane lembuzi elilodwa libe ngumnikelo wesono;
\v 83 lokomhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula, izinkabi ezimbili, inqama ezinhlanu, impongo ezinhlanu, amawundlu amahlanu alomnyaka owodwa. Lokho kwakungumnikelo kaAhira indodana kaEnani.
\p
\v 84 Lokhu kwakuyikwehlukaniselwa kwelathi\x + 7.11.\x* ngosuku lokugcotshwa kwalo ngeziphathamandla zakoIsrayeli. Imiganu yesiliva elitshumi lambili, imiganu yokufafaza yesiliva elitshumi lambili, inkezo zegolide ezilitshumi lambili.
\v 85 Lowo lalowo umganu wesiliva wawungama\add shekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amathathu; langulowo lalowo umganu wokufafaza wamatshumi ayisikhombisa; sonke isiliva semiganu sasingama\add shekeli\add* azinkulungwane ezimbili lamakhulu amane, ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele.
\v 86 Inkezo zegolide ezilitshumi lambili, zigcwele impepha; yilolo lalolokhezo lwalungama\add shekeli\add* alitshumi ngokweshekeli lendlu engcwele; igolide lonke lenkezo lalingama\add shekeli\add* alikhulu lamatshumi amabili.
\v 87 Zonke izifuyo zomnikelo wokutshiswa zazingamajongosi alitshumi lambili, inqama ezilitshumi lambili, amawundlu alomnyaka owodwa alitshumi lambili, lomnikelo wazo wokudla; lamazinyane embuzi alitshumi lambili omnikelo wesono.
\v 88 Lazo zonke izifuyo zomhlatshelo weminikelo yokuthula zazingamajongosi angamatshumi amabili lane, inqama ezingamatshumi ayisithupha, impongo ezingamatshumi ayisithupha, amawundlu angamatshumi ayisithupha alomnyaka owodwa. Lokhu kwakuyikwehlukaniselwa kwelathi\x + 7.11.\x*, emva kokugcotshwa kwalo\x + 7.1,10.\x*.
\p
\v 89 Lapho uMozisi esengena ethenteni lenhlangano ukukhuluma laye, wezwa ilizwi likhuluma kuye\x + 12.8. Eks. 33.9,11.\x*, livela ngaphezu kwesihlalo somusa esiphezu komtshokotsho wobufakazi, livela phakathi \w kwamakherubhi\w** amabili; wasekhuluma kuye\x + Eks. 25.22.\x*.